00286 /* for event checks */
00287     /* only used for KM_TEXTINPUT, so assume that we want all user-inputtable ascii codes included */
00288 #define ISTEXTINPUT(event)  (event >=' ' && event <=255)
00289 
00290     /* test whether the event is a key on the keyboard */
00291 #define ISKEYBOARD(event)   (event >=' ' && event <=320)
00292 
00293     /* test whether the event is a modifier key */
00294 #define ISKEYMODIFIER(event)    ((event >= LEFTCTRLKEY && event <= LEFTSHIFTKEY) || event == OSKEY)
00295 
00296     /* test whether the event is a mouse button */
00297 #define ISMOUSE(event)  (event >= LEFTMOUSE && event <= MOUSEROTATE)
00298 
00299     /* test whether the event is tweak event */
00300 #define ISTWEAK(event)  (event >= EVT_TWEAK_L && event <= EVT_GESTURE)
00301 
00302     /* test whether the event is a NDOF event */
00303 #define ISNDOF(event)   (event >= NDOF_MOTION && event < NDOF_LAST)
00304 
00305 /* test whether event type is acceptable as hotkey, excluding modifiers */
00306 #define ISHOTKEY(event) ((ISKEYBOARD(event) || ISMOUSE(event) || ISNDOF(event)) && event!=ESCKEY && !(event>=LEFTCTRLKEY && event<=LEFTSHIFTKEY) && !(event>=UNKNOWNKEY && event<=GRLESSKEY))
